<lb ed="X" n="0558b21"/><lb ed="R006" n="0794a15"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="82"><cb:jhead>大方廣佛新華嚴經合論卷第八十二</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0558b22"/>
